\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 For your safety, the App analyzes session transcripts to detect signs of acute distress (suicidal ideation, self-harm, abuse, severe addictions). When detected:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
