\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 \strokec2 No external human contact is automatically triggered.
\f1\b0  You remain the sole decision-maker. In case of imminent danger, contact emergency services immediately (112 in Europe, 911 in North America, 143 La Main Tendue in Switzerland, 988 in the US).\
